Name: Crimson Tide: Operation Online
About the game: «Crimson Tide : Operation Online» — is a multiplayer online game that combines the features of FPS, combat simulator and RPG. In the beginning of the game the player is given a random outfit. The same map has random weather conditions. The player's goal is to capture the control point or eliminate the other team.
